 by about 50%, leaving the question open as to whether the\nresidual error is due to deficiencies of the functional, to a neglect of\nnuclear quantum effects in the atomic dynamics, or, likely, to a combination of\nthe two.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2021 17:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 15:49:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2021 10:33:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-24"}
