 computationally efficient; thus this represents a\ngeneral PRF method others can use with deep rerankers and dense retrievers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Aug 2021 04:43:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2022 03:33:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-04"}
