 use the background spectrum produced by the mkacispback tool in an analysis\nof the Cosmic X-ray Background in the CDF-S observations. We find an intensity\nof 3.10 (2.98--$3.21)\\times 10^{-12}$ erg s$^{-1}$ cm$^{-2}$ deg$^{-2}$ in the\n2--8 keV band, consistent with or lower than previous estimates. The tool\nmkacispback is available at https://github.com/hiromasasuzuki/mkacispback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Aug 2021 13:46:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-01"}
